		<p>
			The final site, is very close to the final design. As much as I liked the icons, I think the site looks perfectly fine without them. I added slight images behind the gradients on the homepage, these are tied to the different colors. It's a part of the branding that I've created for the company and works very well on the web. There are SVG that are inlined so there is not extra weight or strain to the site. They are also quite easy to manipulate if I want to change them further on down the road.
		</p>
		<p>
